Rating: 3
I really liked this recipe - I did add a clove of garlic and topped it with parmesan, as I do most of my pasta dishes, and it was very good. I didn't find the sun-dried tomatoes to be overpowering at all, and the Kalamata olives add a lot more flavor than you would think.

